                <h1>Effortless Screen Sharing on Zoom: A Quick Guide</h1>
                <p>To screen share on Zoom, start or join a meeting. Click the "Share Screen" button at the bottom of the window. Select the screen or application you want to share. You can choose to share your entire desktop or just a specific window. When ready, click "Share" and your chosen content will be visible to all participants.</p>
